Неопределенный артикль (Indefinite Article) - A, AN

    -   (one / some / any) в единственным числом всегда / но не во множестовм (a page / pages)
        first time you mention a thing / a person (I saw an old man with a dog)

Определенный артикль (Definite Article) - THE

    -   (this / that)
        already mentioned (I saw a dog. The dog was braking)
        reffering to (My father opend the door)


Отсутсвующий артикль (No article)

    -   in general 
        I love flowers
    -   exception
        (Bed / home / work / town)